{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "3dc0f731-e688-4e54-b5d8-00569278795c",
    "name": "user-api (Kubernetes)",
    "description": "User API with JWT/OAuth2 authentication via Keycloak - Kubernetes Deployment\n\n**Endpoints**:\n- UserAPI: http://localhost:30080 (NodePort)\n- Keycloak: http://localhost:30180 (NodePort)\n\n**Differences from Docker version**:\n- Updated ports for Kubernetes NodePort services\n- Same authentication flow and API endpoints",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "12268386"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Access Token (Password Grant)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('Token response:', json);",
                  "    console.log('Access token found:', json.access_token ? 'YES' : 'NO');",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.access_token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('tokenType', json.token_type);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('expiresIn', json.expires_in);",
                  "    console.log('Token saved to accessToken variable');",
                  "    console.log('Current accessToken value:', pm.collectionVariables.get('accessToken'));",
                  "    ",
                  "    pm.test('K8s: Access token received', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.access_token).to.be.a('string');",
                  "        pm.expect(json.access_token.length).to.be.above(100);",
                  "    });",
                  "    ",
                  "    pm.test('K8s: Token type is Bearer', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.token_type).to.eql('Bearer');",
                  "    });",
                  "    ",
                  "    pm.test('K8s: Token expires in 300 seconds', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.expires_in).to.be.a('number');",
                  "        pm.expect(json.expires_in).to.be.above(0);",
                  "    });",
                  "} else {",
                  "    pm.test('K8s: Status code is 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                {
                  "key": "grant_type",
                  "value": "password",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "client_id",
                  "value": "{{clientId}}",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "client_secret",
                  "value": "{{clientSecret}}",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "username",
                  "value": "admin",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "password",
                  "value": "admin123",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "scope",
                  "value": "openid profile email",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:30180/realms/{{realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/token",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": [
                "localhost"
              ],
              "port": "30180",
              "path": [
                "realms",
                "{{realm}}",
                "protocol",
                "openid-connect",
                "token"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get JWT access token using Resource Owner Password Credentials (ROPC) flow - **Kubernetes Version**\n\n**Grant Type**: password\n**Username**: admin\n**Password**: admin123\n**Keycloak URL**: http://localhost:30180 (Kubernetes NodePort)\n\nThis token will be automatically stored in the `accessToken` variable and used for all subsequent requests."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Access Token (Client Credentials)",
          "event": [
