            "description": "Get JWT access token using Client Credentials flow (service-to-service authentication) - **Kubernetes Version**\n\n**Grant Type**: client_credentials\n**Keycloak URL**: http://localhost:30180 (Kubernetes NodePort)\n\nNote: This flow does not have user context, so token will not include user roles."
